OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchool uniform logos could 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbe scrapped in Wales       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, School uniform logos could be scrapped 
OL,6, in Wales under plans to ease the       
OL,7, financial burden on families.          
OL,9,FThe Welsh government will look at      
OL,10,Fwhether schools should have no logo, or
OL,11,Fuse iron-on logos free of charge.      
OL,13,FIn a letter to governing bodies seen by
OL,14,FBBC Wales, Education Minister Jeremy   
OL,15,FMiles said it would give families the  
OL,16,Foption to purchase uniforms cheaper.   
OL,18,FA public consultation on the proposed  
OL,19,Fchanges will take place "shortly", the 
OL,20,FWelsh government said.                 
